<para id="RM0000012G600AX" category="D" type-id="303F3" name-id="ME02R-08" from="200601">
<name>DIAGNOSIS SYSTEM</name>
<subpara id="RM0000012G600AX_z0" proc-id="RM0250U___00007R900000">
<content5 releasenbr="1">
<step1>
<ptxt>CHECK DLC3</ptxt>
<step2>
<ptxt>The ECU uses ISO 15765-4 for communication. The terminal arrangement of the DLC3 complies with SAE J1962 and matches ISO 15765-4 format. If the result is not as specified, the DLC3 may have a malfunction. Repair or replace harness and connector.</ptxt>
